summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3441, for the improvement of East 51st Street, from Latona Avenue to 5th Avenue Northeast; all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 42718 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
